      "writtenOn": "2021-03-17T06:47:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e\u003e are we doing this only because tests didn\u0027t start a txn?\nNo, it\u0027s not for tests, but the same reason why create_artifacts.go defines the following two functions.\n- verifyStateBeforeWriting()\n- verifyState()\n\ncheckArtStates() and verifyState() are called\n- with a readonly trx in the pre-upload validation, and \n- with a read-write trx in the post-upload validation.\n\nI will add a utility function that calls checkArtStates() w/ read-only trx.",
