      "writtenOn": "2021-03-17T05:35:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "shouldn\u0027t this be InvalidArgument? the problems seems to be that the user sent too much data?\n\nor do you mean we already checked that there wasn\u0027t too much data, but still got this error?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 273,
        "startChar": 32,
